Nigella Lawson will present Simply Nigella on BBC 2 . 
  First time she has appeared on the channel since the breakdown of her marriage to Charles Saatchi in 2012 . 
  Show will focus on 'a new pared-down approach to cooking and eating' The celebrity chef was at the centre of a fraud case involving her two assistants in 2013 . 
  She last appeared on BBC2 in 2012 with Nigellissima . 
 